                    <span>Steven Covey provides the reader a solid roadmap for successful leadership. When leaders with character work with others, they obtain loyalty and inspire the best results. Excellent read.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">7 Habits 14 Points</div>
